<div class="container container--main">
  <h1>Meal Subscription</h1>

  <h4>Din will suggest exciting meals to you each week.</h4>
  <p>Three days before your delivery day, Din will suggest meals via email (and optionally text message). Suggested meals will match your <%= link_to "meal preferences", account_meal_preference_path %>. </p>

  <h4>If youâ€™re excited about the suggested meals, do nothing. </h4>
  <p>The suggested meals will arrive on your delivery day. You will be billed at 5pm the night before your delivery.</p>

  <h4>Want to change the suggested meals, or cancel a delivery? </h4>
  <p>You may change or cancel your order until 5pm the night before your selected delivery, when your order is processed.</p>

  <h4>How much does subscription cost?</h4>
  <p>There is no cost for a subscription other than the cost of meals. Meal prices are set by our restaurant partners and average about $32 ($16/serving). The price of each meal will be included in the email and text message with suggested meals each week.</p>

  <%= form_for @meal_subscription, url: account_meal_subscription_path, method: :post do |f| %>
    <%= render partial: 'form', locals: {f: f} %>
  <% end %>
</div>
